snippet.title: Go Fight Fantastic! - Gameplay Trailer (May 2020)
snippet.description: Go Fight Fantastic! is a super vibrant 3 player co-op adventure game where each player has a unique set of skills. Work together to overcome any and all challenges! For more info, check out https://www.gofightfantastic.com
